title: MARINE CONCRETE STRUCTURES: DESIGN, DURABILITY AND PERFORMANCE
description: Author: Mark Alexander Edition: 1 edition Publication Date: July 9, 2016 Publisher: Woodhead Publishing ISBN-10: 0081009054 ISBN-13: 978-0081009055 Pages: 504 pages Format: pdf Size: 82M --- Marine Concrete Structures: Design, Durability and Performance comprehensively examines structures located in, under, or in close proximity to the sea. A major emphasis of the book is on the long-term performance of marine concrete structures that not only represent major infrastructure investment and provision, but are also required to operate with minimal maintenance. --- http://dlfeb.com/book/marine-concrete-structures-design-durability-and-performance-woodhead-publishing-series-in-civil-and-structural-engineering/
